description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=3/3, Mature Content=0/3. Come and join us ! Let's play volley ball by foot !You can play various actions with using a stick and a button simplly.Tutorial: Learn how to play here.Free play: １st and 2nd set is won by 15 points, third is won by 6 points. A team to win two sets win the match.Tour: Win ten matches each of which is won by a set, which is won by 6 points. you play this mode and will get new costumes.
